## ğŸ”§ Functions Implemented

- `int add(int x, int y)` â€“ Add two integers
- `int sub(int x, int y)` â€“ Subtract two integers
- `int is_even(int n)` â€“ Check if a number is even
- `int reverse_number(int n)` â€“ Reverse a number
- `char convertchar(char c)` â€“ Convert uppercase to lowercase
- `void convert_string(char* str)` â€“ Convert string to lowercase
- `float area_of_circle(int r)` â€“ Calculate area of a circle
- `int find_number_chara(char x, char y)` â€“ Difference in ASCII (count between characters)
- `float ctof(int n)` â€“ Convert Celsius to Fahrenheit
- `int check_leap(int year)` â€“ Check if a year is a leap year
- `int power_n(int n)` â€“ Calculate 2^n using bitwise shift
- `int check_num_char(char s)` â€“ Check if a character is a digit
- `int random_sum()` â€“ Generate 2 random numbers and return their sum

